data.description: Gorgeous home in Warner Robins! This 5 bedroom, 4.5 bath home welcomes you into the formal foyer and features high quality craftsmanship throughout including built-ins, coffered ceilings, archways, and crown molding, a living space on each floor, two kitchens, two laundry rooms, and an open concept floor plan with formal dining room - perfect for entertaining! The main floor kitchen is light, bright, and boasts sprawling center island with wine storage and seating for 8, granite counters, massive pantry, and stainless steel appliance package including built-in oven, and separate gas range - any chef's dream! Relax in the luxurious primary master suite featuring attached office/library, walk-in closet with plentiful built-ins, private back deck, and jetted garden tub with separate shower stall. Nestled on an oversized lot, enjoy warm summer evenings poolside or entertaining in the outdoor barbecue pit. This one won't last!
